data.description: Back on the Market due to HOA Leasing Restrictions. HOA requires ownership for 18 months prior to leasing. Home is perfect for Traditional Buyer. Nestled within the charming Kensington Trace subdivision, this beautiful 2-level home is a testament to comfort and modern living. Offering 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms, it presents the perfect opportunity for a family seeking an idyllic neighborhood and an array of fantastic features. With over 1,700 square feet of well-designed living space, this home offers ample room for your family to grow and flourish. There are 3 generously sized bedrooms provide privacy and comfort for all family members. There are also 2 full bathrooms, along with a convenient half-bath, ensure that your daily routines run smoothly. This home is priced just right, making it an exceptional opportunity for those looking for a perfect blend of value and quality. With all the amenities and space you desire, this home is ready to welcome you and your family.
